    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en">Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'perpendicular curvature' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'curvature'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0015016.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/qualities/Qualities-Morphological/Navicular">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
